 The Government of the Republic of Côte d’Ivoire with the concurrence of the Government of Sri Lanka has appointed Mr. N’dry Eric Camille as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of the Republic of Côte d’Ivoire to Sri Lanka based in New Delhi.  He presented credentials to H.E. Ranil Wickremesinghe, President of Sri Lanka on 02 February 2023 at 3.00 p.m. at the President’s House in Kandy. Distributed by APO Group on behalf of Ministry of Foreign Affairs – Sri Lanka.